
     This subdirectory, \sphere\graph\, contains the graph templates
that were used (with data generated by programs s1 through s8) to
create Figs. 4.2 through 4.6 and Figs. 4.8 through 4.34.  The *.grf
(2D graph) and *.cmd (3D graph) files are used by the GRAPHER (c)
and SURFER (c) graphics programs available from:

